StringValues.16: A letter of introduction to Devana bint Hamudi, who lives near Zaikhal.
StringValues.15: A letter of introduction to Devana bint Hamudi, who lives near Zaikhal.

Pages.Text: Lady Devana, you requested I send to you worthy candidates.  This person has managed to slay one of the great lizards that breathe lightning.  I leave the rest to you.
